== 2010-01-09 v0.9.0 (Release candidate)

* Unlimited subproject nesting
* Multiple roles per user per project
* User groups
* Inheritence of versions
* OpenID login
* "Watched by me" issue filter
* Project copy
* Project creation by non admin users
